      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_052_000038",
    "sentence": "憲之至郡，卽表除之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_052_000039",
    "sentence": "文度後還葬母，郡縣爭赴弔，憲之不與相聞。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_052_000040",
    "sentence": "文度深銜之，卒不能傷也。",
    "entities": [
